tem\" href=\"/host-event\" aria-label=\"Create or host an event\" data-index=\"3\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Host Event</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/contact\" aria-label=\"Open contact page\" data-index=\"4\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Contact</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/login\" aria-label=\"Go to sign in page\" data-index=\"5\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Sign In</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"sm-socials\" aria-label=\"Social links\"><h3 class=\"sm-socials-title\">Socials</h3><ul class=\"sm-socials-list\" role=\"list\"><li class=\"sm-socials-item\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"sm-socials-link\">Instagram</a></li><li class=\"sm-socials-item\"><a href=\"https://linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"sm-socials-link\">LinkedIn</a></li></ul></div></div></aside></div></div><main class=\"page-transition\" style=\"flex:1\"><div class=\"home-page\"><section class=\"home-hero\"><div class=\"container home-hero__content\"><h1 class=\"home-hero__title\">Turn Your Hunches Into<em>Real Benchmarks.</em></h1><p class=\"home-hero__subtitle\">An end-to-end platform to own hackathons, manage challenges, and build real-world solutions</p><div class=\"home-hero__ctas\"><a class=\"home-hero__cta-primary\" href=\"/signup?role=organizer\">For Organizers <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"home-hero__cta-secondary\" href=\"/events\">For Participants <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"home-trust\"><div class=\"container\"><h2 class=\"home-trust__title\">Trusted by leading Organizations &amp; Institutions</h2><div class=\"home-trust__logos\"><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">NASSCOM</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Google</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Microsoft</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Amazon</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Meta</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Adobe</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">IBM</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Intel</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Apple</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Oracle</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Infosys</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">TCS</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">HCL</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Accenture</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-item\">Wipro</div><div class=\"home-trust__logo-more\">→</div></div></div></section><section class=\"home-features\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"home-features__header\"><h2 class=\"home-features__title\">Platform Features That Stand Out</h2><p class=\"home-features__subtitle\">Two focused experiences built for organizers and participants.</p></div><div class=\"home-features__split\"><div class=\"home-features__column home-features__column--organizer\"><h3 class=\"home-features__column-title\">For Organizers</h3><div class=\"home-features__grid\"><div class=\"home-features__card\"><div class=\"home-features__icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-folder-kanban\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><p