R-Based Entry Validation</h4><p class=\"home-features__card-description\">Fast check-in and attendance verification with secure QR scans.</p></div><div class=\"home-features__card\"><div class=\"home-features__icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"home-features__card-title\">Analytics &amp; Insights</h4><p class=\"home-features__card-description\">Track registrations, engagement, and outcomes with clear dashboards.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"home-features__column home-features__column--participant\"><h3 class=\"home-features__column-title\">For Participants</h3><div class=\"home-features__grid\"><div class=\"home-features__card\"><div class=\"home-features__icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h4 class=\"home-features__card-title\">Discover by Interest</h4><p class=\"home-features__card-description\">Find hackathons and challenges that match your goals and skills.</p></div><div class=\"home-features__card\"><div class=\"home-features__icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trophy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 1-.976 1.696A5 5 0 0 0 7 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M14 14.6